Products.description:
From the school-spirited College Colors Program to the vibrant Nike CO.JP collection, Nike Dunks have seen many colorways since the design’s inception in 1985. But with each new colorway, the Dunk’s classic color-blocking has remained in some capacity. Nike put its timeless color-blocking to work with the Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black.

The upper Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black is constructed of white leather with black leather overlays and Swooshes. Classic Nike branding is featured on the nylon tongue, nodding to traditional Dunk design elements. A white midsole and black outsole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black released in January of 2021 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low White Black 2021 women’s sneaker features a white and black leather upper with perforations on the toe box. The base of the upper starts with white leather, and black leather wraps around it in an even pattern. A black Nike Swoosh logo adorns either side of the upper and wraps around the ankle to complete the design.

The Nike Dunk Low White Black 2021 women’s sneaker released in March of 2021 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (W)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black (GS) silhouette comes in a stark black and white colorway and is made from premium leather materials throughout. Additionally, white Nike lettering complements the rear ankle support of the silhouette while the Nike Air text along with the customary company Swoosh logo adorns the tongue. In keeping with the color scheme, a white midsole resting atop a black outsole rounds out the look of this Dunk Low Retro shoe.

The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black (GS) released in March of 2021 and retailed for $85.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (GS)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk High Black White 2021features a smooth white leather upper with perforations on the toe box. Black leather overlays, eyestays and Swooshes match the black laces. Orange hits on the insole add the Total Orange to the vintage White/Black colorway. The rubber outsole is black with a concentric-circles pattern for traction. The midsole is white with visible threading around the shoe. Black Nike branding appears on the white tongue and the heel features a black loop with arcs of white-on-white horizontal threading below it.

  The Nike Dunk High Black White 2021 was released on January 27, 2022 at a retail price of $115.
Products.title: Nike Dunk High Black White (2021)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Premium Vast Grey features a tonal grey suede upper, with warmer tones making up the base while cooler tones make up the overlays. From there, a contrasting cream and grey sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Premium Vast Grey released in August of 2022 and retailed for $110.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Premium Vast Grey

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink has a full leather build, which makes use of three distinct shades of pink to complete the look. The base has a light shade of pink, with a slightly contrasting pink overlay.

The look is completed by the Nike Swoosh in a bold pink that provides a strong contrast and stands out noticeably on the shoe. In addition to the Swoosh on both sides, the Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink (Grade School) features Nike branding on the sole, heel, tongue, and inner sole. This shoe comes in Grade School (GS) sizing.

The Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink (Grade School) was released in early June, 2022, at the retail price of $85.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink (GS)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk features an off-white tumbled leather upper with pale yellow overlays and white Swooshes. Woven tongue labels and heel embroideries nod to the original 1985 design. From there, a matching Air sole at the base completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk released in March of 2022 and retailed for $100.

DISCLAIMER: Yellow may appear different in various lighting situations.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk

Products.description:
The Swoosh on the Nike Dunk Low Judge Grey is white, as are the laces and the Nike logo on the tongue.

This low-top sneaker has a full leather construction with a mocha-brown base color that’s complemented by a lighter overlay around the heel, where the laces go through and around the toe. The Nike Dunk Low Judge Grey’s sole matches the lighter hue on the overlays, but it also has a white highlight between the base of the sole and the shoe itself.

The Nike Dunk Low Judge Grey sneaker was made available for retail at a price of $100 in June, 2022.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Judge Grey
Nike Dunk Low Medium Olive (W)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Racer Blue White features a smooth Racer Blue leather upper with contrasting white leather overlays and Swooshes. A woven Nike tongue tag and heel embroidery nod to the original stylings of the 1985 Nike Dunk. At the base, a matching EVA foam sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Racer Blue White released in 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Racer Blue White

Products.description:
The women's Nike Dunk Low Safari Mix (W) explores exotic patterns and textures with its one-of-a-kind construction. Atop a white leather base, the upper features vibrant overlays constructed of leopard-pattern Durabuck, safari print, faux-horsehair, suede, and smooth leather. Vintage-style Nike woven tongue labels add the finishing touch.

The women's Nike Dunk Low Safari Mix (W) released in March of 2022 and retailed for $120.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Safari Mix (W)

Products.description:
The women's Nike Dunk Low Rose Whisper arrives in a classic two-tone color blocked look similar to the original Nike Dunks of the 1980s. This Dunk offers a warm palette primed for the summer weather, with a white and Rose Whisper leather construction. Matching woven tongue labels contribute to the design's retro feel, while an EVA foam sole provides cushioning.

The women's Nike Dunk Low Rose Whisper released in June of 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Rose Whisper (W)

Products.description:
The women's Nike Dunk High Panda (W) features white and black leather upper with a matching sole. From there, hits of red on the woven tongue label add some subtle flair.

The women's Nike Dunk High Black White (W) released in July of 2021 and retailed for $110.
Products.title: Nike Dunk High Panda (2021) (W)
Nike SB Dunk High FAUST Black Gold

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Valerian Blue arrives in a smooth white leather construction with deep Valerian Blue overlays and Swooshes. Hits of red on the woven tongue label and heel embroidery add a subtle contrast. At the base, a matching white and blue Air sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Valerian Blue released in May of 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Valerian Blue
Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Lilac (W)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Chlorophyll features a light green smooth leather upper with darker green overlays and white Swooshes. Woven tongue labels and Nike embroideries on the heel tabs add a retro look. At the base, a white and green foam sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Chlorophyll released in 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Chlorophyll

Products.description:
Nike Sportswear added to their Dunk Low lineup with this Nike Dunk Low Two Toned Grey with grade school sizing (GS) colorway, arriving in a mix of gray tones. The Nike Dunk Low Two Toned Grey (GS) comes constructed in a full leather build featuring light and dark shades of gray. The clean two-toned Grey colorway sees the slightly darker shade of neutral overlaying the base layer, while the white Swoosh logo, laces, and midsole complete the two-tone look. A gray rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Two Toned Grey (GS) was released in March of 2022 at a retail price of $85.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Two-Toned Grey (GS)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black PS features an entirely white leather upper with black overlays. The touches of black continue to the Swoosh branding, and the vintage basketball shoe is finished off with a padded collar and nylon mesh tongue, a white midsole, and a black outsole and treading. 

The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black PS was released in March 2021 and originally retailed for $65.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (PS)

Products.description:
In celebration of the 75th Anniversary of the NBA, Nike teamed up with the NBA to release a Chicago Bulls-themed Nike Dunk Low.

The Nike Dunk Low EMB 75th Anniversary Chicago features a Sail leather upper with a red toe wrap and black overlays. From there, a commemorative NBA logo woven tongue tags and matching sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low EMB 75th Anniversary Chicago released in October of 2021 and retailed for $110.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low EMB NBA 75th Anniversary Chicago

Products.description:
A toddler’s shoe (TD), the Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black TD comes in a classic colorway. Crafted from soft leather, the Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black (TD) upper is made from a white base overlaid by contrasting black throughout. The black extends to the iconic Swoosh branding and the lightly padded nylon tongue. The tooling continues the two-toned design to include a white midsole and a black rubber outsole that draws directly from the Air Jordan 1.

The Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black (TD) was released in March 2021 at a retail price of $50.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (TD)
Nike Dunk Low World Champs Black White

Products.description:
While the Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson is not an official collaboration with The Simpsons, it channels color inspiration to the rambunctious character and follows a similar format to the Nike SB Dunk High Marge Simpson and the Nike SB Dunk Low Homer Simpson.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson features a yellow leather upper with orange Durabuck overlays and a white Swoosh. Hits of blue on the sock liner and outsole add a cool-toned contrast to the shoe's warm palette. At the base, a Zoom sole provides comfort and support.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Bart Simpson released in May of 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro Bart Simpson
Nike Dunk Low Reverse UNC (W)

Products.description:
The women's Nike Dunk Low Venice (W) features a smooth white leather upper with light violet overlays and Swooshes. From there, matching woven tongue labels and soles complete the design.

The women's Nike Dunk Low Venice (W) released in February of 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Venice (W)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Reverse Panda features the Nike Swoosh logo in black on the tongue and also on the heel padding behind the ankle.

The Nike Dunk Low Reverse Panda has a clean white color throughout, including the sole, with contrasting touches of black. The shoe also features a lace-up closure style with black laces. The Nike Swoosh is found on both sides, also in black, and these meet behind the ankle and below the white heel padding.

The Nike Dunk Low Reverse Panda first debuted in Asia in June, 2022, and then in the UK and Europe in July of 2022 at a retail price of $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Reverse Panda

Products.description:
Constructed of white and Team Red smooth leather, the Nike Dunk Low Team Red is an ode to the original look of the 1985 Nike Dunk Low. Nike embroideries on the heel tab and a woven tongue label arrive in a classic fashion. From there, a white and Team Red sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Team Red released in May of 2022 and retailed for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Team Red (2022)
Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Homer Simpson (GS)
Nike Dunk Low Patent Halloween (W)

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Arctic Orange features a unique, tonal construction of warm woven fabrics and light green tumbled leather overlays. At the heel, a "Nike Sun Club" embroidery adds to the shoes warm-weather theme. A white and speckled light green Air sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Arctic Orange released in May of 2022 and retailed for $110.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Sun Club Arctic Orange

Products.description:
The Nike SB Dunk Low Los Angeles Dodgers features a white leather upper with blue overlays and red Swoosh logos. The "Nike" brand name is prevanlent on the heel tab in red.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Los Angeles Dodgers is a low-top sneaker with lace-up closure style. The shoe features a blue and white color scheme that has shades similar to the traditional blue and white worn by the MLB's LA Dodgers. It has a light-brown sole with a pink graphic on the ankle’s right side.

The Nike SB Dunk Low Los Angeles Dodgers was released in June of 2022 at the retail price of $110.
Products.title: Nike SB Dunk Low Los Angeles Dodgers

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low Championship Purple features a white leather upper with Championship Purple overlays and Swooshes. Nike embroidery at the heel pays tribute to the original 1985 design. At the base, a white and purple sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Dunk Low Championship Purple releases in May of 2022 and retails for $100.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Championship Court Purple

Products.description:
The Nike Dunk Low PRM Cider features a dark navy and Cider nubuck and suede upper with Dark Chocolate smooth leather overlays and Swooshes. At the heel, a Wild Berry leather patch boasts Nike embroidery. At the base, an Off Noir and Dark Chocolate Air sole completes the design.

The Nike Dunk Low PRM Cider released in May of 2022 and retailed for $110.
Products.title: Nike Dunk Low Cider
